{
  "stem": "27285.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, what I remember most is not the huge, tragic big things, because this-- but the small things that they could invent to torment us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is really-- we were for three, four days on the way-- I don't remember again-- and we were quite where we didn't have any food on the way, on this little way.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came there, and they sat us down and they put a huge bowl of soup or whatever it was, and we couldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all those other inmates standing around and implying-- imploring us to eat, because otherwise they will shorten the rations again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't explain it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whether it's the nature of a person that fasts for a few days that he can't immediately start wolfing food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also he's so hungry that he is so weak that he can't react to this at all in a normal way, or maybe eat three spoonfuls and then that's it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was like proof that you don't need so much food, and then they could-- you see, it was all those little things.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This laments in your memory that human beings-- that it is possible for human beings to become such callous and such a person.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was mostly-- it's also-- it was-- it's actually [? where ?] women around that were-- we were under their command.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is my first impression of Oederan, which is the new place, the new concentration camp where we landed now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was Oederan, and we were thrown into-- I don't know how you call it such.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Wooden pallets.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a little straw on it, and we were two or three together on a very small space.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
